## Installation

To install the CLI, ensure you have Go installed and run:

```bash
go install .
```

## Authentication

This CLI supports multiple authentication profiles. To add a new profile, use:

```bash
{{ .Name }} auth add-profile <name> [auth-params]
```

To list available profiles:

```bash
{{ .Name }} auth list-profiles
```

To use a specific profile for a command:

```bash
{{ .Name }} --profile <name> [command]
```

